{"tid":1125128,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Nokia 9 PureView 拍片分享 指紋辨識形同虛設","createTime":"2019-04-25T13:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T00:34:17.000Z","uid":23677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8528430555a1a2b715e422584792c1d2f3a52957","tid":1125128,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:12:10.000Z","msg":"Nokia 9 PureView 上市至今，不可靠的指紋辨識是用戶投訴最多的功能，上星期 HMD Global 終於推出針對指紋辨識推出更新。部分用戶表示在安裝更新後，功能有所改善，但亦有用戶表示相反，更新後的指紋辨識功能形同虛設，幾乎可以用任何物品將之解鎖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pefmb0h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPefmb0h.jpg&h=c56bab4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其中一名用戶@decodedpixel 睇過 Twitter 分享他的 Nokia 9 PureView，在更新後竟然可以被沒有登記的他人手指，甚至一排香口膠將之解鎖。他表示曾經試過以硬幣和一對皮手套，同樣可以通過 Nokia 9 PureView 的指紋辨識，就算是他重新登記指紋亦無補於事。雖然從影片可見，他的手機貼上了玻璃保護貼，有機會影響指紋辨識的效果，但任何物品都可以解鎖卻並不合理。<br />\n<br />\n暫時 HMD Global 未有就事件作出回應，未知道上述情況是否只有該名用戶的手機剛巧有問題，還是更新後系統有漏洞所致。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/unwire.hk/2019/04/24/nokia-9-pureviews-fingerprint-sensor-opened-by-a-pack-of-gum/mobile-phone/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F04%2F24%2Fnokia-9-pureviews-fingerprint-sensor-opened-by-a-pack-of-gum%2Fmobile-phone%2Famp%2F&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreM22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=058d93a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/unwire.hk/2019/04/24/nokia-9-pureviews-fingerprint-sensor-opened-by-a-pack-of-gum/mobile-phone/amp/</a>"},{"pid":"02339d8e8767682f1c0131372d99a91dc89af941","tid":1125128,"uid":5846,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:28:01.000Z","msg":"Iphone Faceid又贏"},{"pid":"194797dd3baf52e59ca34bcbc45f03705beba64a","tid":1125128,"uid":158977,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"02339d8e8767682f1c0131372d99a91dc89af941","tid":1125128,"uid":5846,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:28:01